Package net.edudb.structure.table

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Table  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryTable  
    BinaryTableReader
    A table information reader that reads binary table information files from disk.
    BinaryTableWriter
    A table information writer that writes binary table information files to disk.
    TableAbstractFactory
    An abstract factory that creates both table information reader and writer factories.
    TableFactory
    A factory that creates table information file types supported by EduDB.
    TableManager
    TableManager is a singleton that is a wrapper class around TableAbstractFactory.
    TableReader
    A reader that reads table's information files.
    TableReaderFactory
    A factory that creates table information readers.
    TableWriter
    A writer that writes table's information files to disk.
    TableWriterFactory
    A factory that creates table information writers.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TableFileType
    Supported table information file types.
